extendedInfo.description: StarCraft Byte (zerg) is a sound clip application for android phones, contains sound clip of all Star Craft 2 units:BanelingBroodlingBroodlordChangelingCorruptorDroneHydraliskInfested TerranInfestorLurkerMutaliskOverlordOverseerQueenRoachUltraliskZergling********** Read me first **********all starcraft and starcraft 2 logo/s, image/s, audio/s & character/s are properties of its respective owner, the developer does not take credit for any of those mentioned above, and any third party files used in making this application like images and sound effects are also properties of their respective owners.All trademarks referenced herein are the properties of their respective owners. Â©2011 All rights reserved.******************************************** Notice **********This application is the same as the old StarCraft Byte(Zerg), with the patch 1.1 included, due to some problems during development, i had to unpublish and deactivate the old application and had to upload a new one, in short this now  is the permanent application, so you can now uninstall the old application and download this one instead. If the audio for any units happens to not play after pressing the button just return to the main menu and just access the said button again and it will play now, just a minor glitch in the system, and a very easy solution is to just re access that page again just by going back and again, i no longer make sense so just have fun with it! :DStarCraft Byte "by a fan for the fans"****************************
